snippet.title: Pokémon Rumble U Trailer
snippet.description: In Pokémon Rumble U, you'll be able to experience amazingly vivid battles packed with many Pokémon on the Wii U. You may find yourself in a battle with up to 100 Pokémon at a time! http://bit.ly/12Y3WWB
